import React from 'react' import '../styles/tour-details.css' import {Container, Row,Col,Form,ListGroup} from 'reactstrap' import {useParams} from 'react-router-dom' import tourData from '../assets/data/tours' const TourDetails = () => { const {id} = useParams() // This is an Static Data later we will call our API and load our data from database const tour =tourData.find(tour=> tour.id===id) // destructure props from tour object const {photo,title ,desc, price,reviews,city,distance, maxGroupSize} = tour return <>
'

{title}
} export default TourDetails
